'''卡納達文'''({{lang-kn|ಕನ್ನಡ ಅಕ್ಷರಮಾಲೆ}} {{IAST|Kannaḍa akṣaramāle}})是[[婆羅米系文字|婆羅米系]][[元音附標文字|元音附標文字]]<ref>{{cite book | title = Handbook of scripts and alphabets | url = https://archive.org/details/routledgehandboo00camp | first = George L. | last = Campbell | publisher = [[Routledge|Routledge]], [[Newyork|Newyork]] | date = 1997-11-06 | edition = 1st Ed. | accessdate = 2007-02-23 | pages = [https://archive.org/details/routledgehandboo00camp/page/n47 84]–5 | isbn = 9780415137157 | oclc = 34473667}}</ref>，主要用來書寫[[卡納達語|卡納達語]]，它是[[印度|印度]]的[[達羅毗荼語系|達羅毗荼語]]之一。它也用於[[孔卡尼語|孔卡尼語]]、Tulu語、Beary語和Kodava語。

==歷史==
卡納達（Kannada）文派生自古卡納達文。<ref>{{cite web
|url=http://www.ancientscripts.com/kannada.html
|title=Kannada
|publisher=
|accessdate=2009-05-07
|archive-date=2012-02-08
|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/65IUc0wjN?url=http://www.ancientscripts.com/kannada.html
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>古卡納達文是公元10世紀的[[Kadamba文|Kadamba文]]的延續<ref>{{cite web
|url=http://www.ancientscripts.com/old_kannada.html
|title=Old Kannada
|publisher=
|accessdate=2009-05-07
|archive-date=2012-02-08
|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/65IUcgTOF?url=http://www.ancientscripts.com/old_kannada.html
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>，它用來書寫[[卡納達語|卡納達語]]和[[泰盧固語|泰盧固語]]，也叫做[[泰盧固-卡納達文|泰盧固-卡納達文]]。現代的卡納達文和泰盧固文早在公元13世紀前就分離了。

[[Kadamba文|Kadamba文]]演化自[[婆羅米文|婆羅米文]]（在公元5世紀）。<ref>{{cite web
|url=http://www.ancientscripts.com/kadamba.html
|title=Kadamba
